des: by sharing our personal stories, we allow ourselves a chance to heal through sharing, while at the same time helping others who might be going through similar things. Stories make us feel less alone, they offer hope and can bring us together. When you share your story with us, you own it. We don’t change it. We post it anonymously - because we know that domestic violence can affect anyone and everyone.
